title: Sri Lankan Potato & Cauliflower Dhal with Garlic Tortilla Chips
description: Be sure your cutlery is at the ready because this dhal is going to disappear in seconds. It has everything, roasted
cauliflower, carrot and a creamy taste. Dip the garlic tortilla chips in for a bit of fun and flavour.

